title: Ep 23: Thunderous Dad Pee
description:
Today's Proceedings:  Some one learns where babies come from a little too late, two stories of bros preventing their bros from getting some, and a theatre kid who can't stop one upping.  We also discuss the world's oldest question: are boobs overrated?
